<item>
            <title>[LU-3500] must use __u64 when handling sp_cr_flags</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3500</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;struct md_op_spec&apos;s member sp_cr_flags is a __u64 mask which is actually used &lt;br/&gt;
to store some flags the will not fit in __u32, for example MDS_OPEN_VOLATILE = 0400000000000ULL = 0x800000000. Code that copies this field should use __u64 and not __u32 as occurs in some places.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
